snippet.title: Legions: Overdrive - 10 Year Reunion
snippet.description:
Can you believe it's been 10 years since Legions released? We sure as hell can't. Why not celebrate by playing a full night of games with the community?!

This Saturday, June 23rd at 8pm EST, join us in the Legions Discord to reminisce and celebrate one of the greatest shooters ever made.

https://discord.gg/legions

https://www.legionsoverdrive.com/download/
